{"tid":353934,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"用左咁多年,突然感覺好似俾人呃左","createTime":"2017-08-10T04:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T01:34:06.000Z","uid":6848,"like":361,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b484594fe44ad7a61f6173bcc570cf04468094d1","tid":353934,"uid":6848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"幾年前喺衛訊用左500$買左隻Lightning手指，<br />\n原意係方便自己電腦過野落電話。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/122351_1e46fc49cad7f4037d6a1aa96baf6cbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F122351_1e46fc49cad7f4037d6a1aa96baf6cbb.jpg&h=f753ad4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日朝無啦啦lightning頭嗰邊讀唔到無反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上下兩個頭仲有啲鬆鬆地，<br />\n我大力少少成條扯左出黎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/122615_156b1c3e0b93e92683808cac45ab0774.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F122615_156b1c3e0b93e92683808cac45ab0774.jpg&h=03e0f533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/122836_d3101256676786997ead765954cf9f37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F122836_d3101256676786997ead765954cf9f37.jpg&h=d216ef34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆你個街原來放張Micro SD卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頓時發覺當年買個Lightning SD cardreader + 一張32GB卡都只係2xx-3xx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似比人呃左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124ca42c277b1e55d9af4c6d748a678bbb1184b5","tid":353934,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"是"},{"pid":"2fdfe9f863f4bfb2fdc1bf8207c5f9205ce091da","tid